title: World On Watch
summary: Over 2000+ collection of world's best destinations on your smart watch
description: World on Watch(WoW) is an breathtaking smartwatch application that will bring the top 30 destinations of the world on your smartwatchThe unique features of the app are:- All Watch faces absolutely "Free".- Analog and Digital Dials- Digital dial text direction: Top, Center, Bottom- Over 20 Digital fonts available- Beautiful collections of over 2000 images covering the following destinations  - Amsterdam  - Argentina  - Australia  - Belgium  - Brazil   - Budapest  - California  - Canada   - China  - Dubai  - Egypt  - Germany  - Hawaii  - India  - Italy  - Japan  - Las Vegas  - London  - Mauritius  - New York  - New Zealand  - Norway  - Paris  - Russia  - Singapore  - South Africa  - South Korea  - Spain  - Switzerland  - ThailandNote : Only supports Android Wear Watches.(Watches like Samsung Gear, DZ09 ,Sony smartwatch are not supported)
descriptionHTML:
World on Watch(WoW) is an breathtaking smartwatch application that will bring the top 30 destinations of the world on your smartwatch

The unique features of the app are:

- All Watch faces absolutely "Free".
- Analog and Digital Dials
- Digital dial text direction: Top, Center, Bottom
- Over 20 Digital fonts available
- Beautiful collections of over 2000 images covering the following destinations
- Amsterdam
- Argentina
- Australia
- Belgium
- Brazil
- Budapest
- California
- Canada
- China
- Dubai
- Egypt
- Germany
- Hawaii
- India
- Italy
- Japan
- Las Vegas
- London
- Mauritius
- New York
- New Zealand
- Norway
- Paris
- Russia
- Singapore
- South Africa
- South Korea
- Spain
- Switzerland
- Thailand

Note : Only supports Android Wear Watches.
(Watches like Samsung Gear, DZ09 ,Sony smartwatch are not supported)
